Explain CloudWatch Events to a non-technical friend.
      CloudWatch Events acts as a central message distributer for your AWS infrastructure, enabling you to monitor events and trigger actions based on specific conditions. It helps automate workflows, respond to events, and improve resource responsiveness.

What do CloudWatch Logs helps us achieve?
      CloudWatch Logs facilitates log collection and analysis, to effectively monitor, troubleshoot systems, and AWS services.


What capabilities does CloudWatch Anomaly detection have?
      CloudWatch Anomaly Detection uses machine learning to identify anomalous patterns, enabling you to proactively detect and address potential issues before they impact your applications or systems.
